SQS:- simple queue service
1) it is fully managed messages queuing
2) that enables differnet application & services to commuincate with each other relability


USES OF SQS:- 
         1) mesage queuing
         2) decoupling apllication
         3) load balancing workloads 
         4) improve realibitly


TYPES OF SQS:- 
     1) standard queue
     2) fifo queue

1) STANDARD QUEUE:- 
           best effort ordering (mesaages might be deliverd out of order)
           use for:- background jobs , notifications , asynchronous workloads

2) FIFO QUEUE:- 
           first in first out
           exactly_once processing
           use for:- payment system , order processing , workflow system
